# Dataset Access

This study uses publicly available Bitcoin blockchain traces obtained from the Google BigQuery Public Datasets program.

Dataset:
Google BigQuery Public Bitcoin Dataset

Project:
bigquery-public-data

Relevant Tables:

* crypto_bitcoin.blocks
* crypto_bitcoin.transactions

The dataset can be accessed through Google BigQuery:

https://console.cloud.google.com/marketplace/product/bigquery-public-data/crypto-bitcoin

The dataset is not redistributed in this repository due to its large size and public availability.
